        <div class="item-meta">
          9 points &bull; <a href="/user/mijustin">mijustin</a> &bull; 19 hours ago &bull; 6 comments
        </div>
        <div class="item-text">I&#x27;m curious about what&#x27;s going on in the agency world right now.<p>I worked at web agencies for a lot of my career, and I&#x27;m thinking about the kinds of projects we would get: build a website, build a simple app, build internal tools, maintain a WordPress site, build a website theme, etc...<p>It feels like a lot of that is being taken over by LLMs and tools like Claude Code? Are agencies feeling cooked right now?<p>If you&#x27;re at an agency, what&#x27;s happening in your world?</div>
        <div class="item-actions">
          <a class="comment-button" href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47770115">Write a comment on HN</a>
        </div>
